    "E-measure (E φ).",
    "Enhanced-measure [100] is used to evaluate region coverage.E φ = (1 + φ 2) • S O • S R φ 2 • S O + S R,( 6)where the parameter φ is a balancing parameter that adjusts the weight ratio between accuracy and region coverage.",
    "= 1 W × H W ∑ i=1 H ∑ j=1 |S i,j -G i,j |,( 7)where W and H denote the width and height of the map, S represents the predicted segmentation map, and G represents the ground truth segmentation map.",
